ses it may indicate a householder, steward at a castle, or the watchman on a tower. This surname is also found in France (Alsace and Lorraine). Compare   Haushalter  ."]},{"name":"Hauss","meanings":["Some characteristic forenames:  French Jacques, Pierre.","German: variant of   Haus  . This surname is also found in France (Alsace and Lorraine)."]},{"name":"Hause","meanings":["German: variant of   Haus  ."]}]},{"name":"Liefhard","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["variant of   Leonhard ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Liefhard von Ahaus was born about 1105, in Germany as the son of Bernhard van Diepenheim. He had at least 1 son with Kunigunde von Versfleth. He died after 1154."},"et":{"Abt 1105–Aft 1154":"umbes 1105–pärast 1154","1105–1154":"1105–1154","1125–1198":"1125–1198","1140–1221":"1140–1221","1075–1139":"1075–1139","1139":"1139","1105":"1105","Aft 1154":"pärast 1154","1125":"1125","about 1139":"umbes 1139","1221":"1221","1198":"1198","1154":"1154","Abt 1105":"umbes 1105","1075":"1075","1140":"1140","Germany":"Saksamaa","Ahaus, Westfalen, Preußen, Duitsland":"Kreis Ahaus, Provinz Westfalen, Preußen"},"fi":{"Abt 1105–Aft 1154":"noin 1105–1154 jälkeen","1105–1154":"1105–1154","1125–1198":"1125–1198","1140–1221":"1140–1221","1075–1139":"1075–1139","1139":"1139","1105":"1105","Aft 1154":"1154 jälkeen","1125":"1125","about 1139":"noin 1139","1221":"1221","1198":"1198","1154":"1154","Abt 1105":"noin 1105","1075":"1075","1140":"1140","Germany":"Saksa","Ahaus, Westfalen, Preußen, Duitsland":"Kreis Ahaus, Provinz Westfalen, Preußen"},"fr":{"Abt 1105–Aft 1154":"environ 1105–après 1154","1105–1154":"1105–1154","1125–1198":"1125–1198","1140–1221":"1140–1221","1075–1139":"1075–1139","1139":"1139","1105":"1105","Aft 1154":"après 1154","1125":"1125","about 1139":"environ 1139","1221":"1221","1198":"1198","1154":"1154","Abt 1105":"environ 1105","1075":"1075","1140":"1140","Germany":"Allema